title: BUCK-O-NINE DISCOGRAPHY 1994-2007! (MP3 @ 256 kbps VBR)
description:
Here it is! The entire collection of one of the greatest ska bands of all time!

All releases are 256 kbps VBR, ripped from genuine CD source by yours truly (unless otherwise noted)! All releases have covers, too! Most can be found online, but I scanned the cover On a Mission because there are no good quality ones out there. Hopefully mine will suffice.

I put a lot of time and money into this, so please seed this longer than you enjoy it!

Also, this is my first discography, so hopefully everything is in order and set up the way you guys like it! I was going to scan all the booklets from all the releases, but that was gonna take too long, so instead I just upped what you guys care about -- THE MUSIC!

===5 Albums===
1994 - Songs in the Key of Bree
1995 - Barfly
1997 - Twenty-Eight Teeth
1999 - Libido
2007 - Sustain

===2 EPs===
1996 - Water in My Head
1998 - Pass the Dutchie

===3 Miscellaneous (1 Live Album + 1 Import + 1 Compilation)===
1997 - The Duran Duran Tribute Album [MP3, 128 kbps] (Only includes the Buck-O-Nine cover of "Hold Back the Rain")
2000 - Hellos & Goodbyes (Live and Unreleased)
2001 - On a Mission (Import)

Learn more about Buck-O-Nine's releases here: <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buck-O-Nine" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buck-O-Nine</a>

It includes their discography with track listings.
